e":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I prayed with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, two prostrations before and after noon prayer, two prostrations after sunset prayer, two prostrations after evening prayer, and two prostrations after Friday prayer. As for sunset and evening prayer, they were in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31747,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/in-salat-waiting-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":17429,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: You are in prayer if you are waiting for prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: We prayed with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, at nightfall and he did not come out until half of the night had passed. The Prophet said, \u201cTake your places.\u201d We took our places and the Prophet said, \u201cVerily, people have prayed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36430,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/nawafil-after-salat-al-isha\/","url_meta":{"origin":17429,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary raka\u2019at after Isha prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, never